@node "INFO" "SN QWiK Menu v1.0 - Information"
@toc "MAIN"
┌─────────────────────────────────┐
  SN QWiK Menu v1.0 - Information
└─────────────────────────────────┘

   The concept of this utility was introduced to me by Hacker Cat's (tm)
version of a .QWK packet menu.  I've spruced it up a bit, made it a little
nicer looking and modified the idea to suit my needs.  (I wrote this from
scratch, not using any previously written code.)

Features to note:
  - Path self-aware.
  - Seperate headers and menu systems for ASCII and ANSI users.  The ANSI
    menu is pretty nice!
  - Provides the user the option to change their compression format,
    download new, all or since a certain date messages and finally,
    upload their .REP packets.

───SN/AHI (910) 326-3804 (28.8k)─────────────────────────────────────────
@endnode
